            <p class="editorial-body">For all who believe intelligence is not just speed or code, but <strong>resonance</strong>, <strong>intention</strong>, and <strong>imagination</strong>.</p>
            <p class="editorial-body">We don't segment humans. We speak across ages, across roles, across disciplines.</p>
            <p class="editorial-body">We create for those who sense that something is shifting — and want to <strong>move with purpose</strong>.</p>
            <p class="editorial-body">For those who wish to be <strong>free in their mind</strong>, in their heart, and in their life.</p>
          </div>
